<p><b>Ian Russell McEwan</b>,<sup id="cite_ref-filmr_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-filmr-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> <a href="/wiki/CBE" title="CBE" class="mw-redirect">CBE</a>, <a href="/wiki/Royal_Society_of_Arts" title="Royal Society of Arts" class="mw-redirect">FRSA</a>, <a href="/wiki/Royal_Society_of_Literature" title="Royal Society of Literature">FRSL</a>, (born 21 June 1948) is a <a href="/wiki/Booker_Prize" title="Booker Prize" class="mw-redirect">Booker Prize</a>-winning <a href="/wiki/England" title="England">English</a> <a href="/wiki/Novelist" title="Novelist" class="mw-redirect">novelist</a> and <a href="/wiki/Screenwriter" title="Screenwriter">screenwriter</a>.</p>
